snippet.title: Conan the Barbarian - (1985) - Bally Astrocade - gameplay
snippet.description:
Bally Midway © 1985
[Console] Bally Astrocade
Emulator: MAME 0.226

Well here is something at least different and interesting, if not very good.  Taken from the hit movie, play a warrior killing those evil snakes and spiders!  Yeah, go Conan!  Survive each wave of deadly insects, and you can advance to another level.  Hah.  Well, at least they put in some cool battle sounds.  Swinging the axe is weird and dumb, though.  Level 7.
